312
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:56,200
I’m just in a relationship with your daughter.

313
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:03,680
I went to buy vegetables.

314
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:05,760
I did the cooking.

315
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,240
I wash the plates

316
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:09,440
