353
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:55,420
Bah!

354
00:18:56,620 --> 00:18:58,460
He's such a scumbag!

355
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:00,600
Honey,

356
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,360
