523
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:51,730
What is that?

524
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,760
Drink it.

525
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:56,080
Very nutritious rice noodles!

526
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:00,080
Mom,

527
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:02,480
