00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:27,280
40 yuan for two bags.

789
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:27,920
Ok.

790
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:28,920
Here you are.

791
00:35:29,720 --> 00:35:30,640
Thank you.

792
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,120
Yuanyuan,

793
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:34,120
