848
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:54,840
But I know that

849
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:57,400
she was afraid I may worry about her.

850
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:59,080
But that made me

851
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:01,440
