857
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:15,560
Mrs. Jiang,

858
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:16,960
go ahead.

859
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:19,080
I hope that

860
00:38:19,640 --> 00:38:21,400
no matter how

861
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:23,200
